These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Game: chess, scrabble, backgammon, whist
1. Game:scrabble is in an odd position##4
2. Game:whist is between Game:chess and Game:scrabble##2
3. Game:whist is on the right of Game:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | chess | whist | scrabble | backgammon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: writing, board-games, dancing, video-games
1. Hobby:writing is on the left of Hobby:video-games##1
2. Hobby:board-games is in an odd position##4
3. Hobby:board-games is on the left or right of Hobby:writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby   | board-games | writing | video-games | dancing |

 #################################
 
