.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
City: miami, berlin, boston, marseilles
1. City:miami is in an even position##4
2. City:boston is on the right of City:miami##1
3. City:berlin is on the left or right of City:boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| City   | marseilles | miami | boston | berlin |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
Music-Genre: folk, jazz, techno, electronic
1. Music-Genre:jazz is on the far right##1
2. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:electronic##3
3. Music-Genre:techno is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | folk | electronic | jazz |

