.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Hobby: traveling, gardening, card-games, fishing
1. Hobby:gardening == Hobby:gardening##1
2. Hobby:fishing is on the left or right of Hobby:card-games##3
3. Hobby:card-games is on the far left or far right##3
4. Hobby:traveling is in an even position##4
5. Hobby:fishing is on the left of Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | card-games | fishing | gardening | traveling |

 #################################
 
